# Cursor: skip huge or generated trees (reduces lag)
**/.git/
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/DerivedData/
**/Pods/
**/.firebase/
**/__pycache__/

# Xcode
*.xcresult/
*.app/
*.dSYM/

# macOS duplicate copies (Finder "name 2") — never need these indexed
**/* 2/
**/* 3/

# Logs / backups
Project Planner_backup_*/
build.log
*.patch

# Agent tooling noise
.cursor/projects/**/agent-tools/
